title: Electronics - Circuits and Systems, 4th Edition
description:
English | 2011 | ISBN: 0080966349 | PDF | 382 pages | 9,7 MB

Electronics-Circuits and Systems is a truly up-to-date textbook, with coverage carefully matched to the electronics units of the BTEC National Engineering course.

The material has been organized with a logical learning progression, making it ideal for a wide range of pre-degree courses in electronics.
